  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Deployed 3/2/2020 11:30PM CT (16:30 UTC)</p><p>Release 1.16.24 is a minor release which adds a handful of new features and bug fixes.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.16.24-NewFeaturesandEnhancements\">New Features and Enhancements</h3><ul><li><p>Invoice Created On Date can now be printed on invoices through a new print setting.</p></li><li><p>RepairQ will now prevent changing the item type for already used items via catalog item import.</p></li><li><p>Auto clock out will now set the clock out time with more precision.</p></li><li><p>RepairQ will now auto-close appointments when a quote is converted, and convert a quote when an appointment is started.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.16.24-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>We fixed a handful of issues with capturing electronic signatures on Qpop.</p></li><li><p>Fixed confusing input focus change on serial number input for Trade-in items.</p></li><li><p>Fixed issue with searching some special characters.</p></li><li><p>Fixed error when geocoding locations in Qsite settings.</p></li><li><p>Fixed Summary Report layout issue when viewed from beginning of year.</p></li><li><p>Fixed the ability to clear customer info by saving empty values for customer attributes.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue where timesheet totals were incorrect if a staff member clocked in at multiple locations for the same time period.</p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
